Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.74,0:47:36.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.00,0:47:39.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.58,0:47:44.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.79,0:47:46.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.51,0:47:56.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.52,0:48:00.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.39,0:48:04.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.27,0:48:09.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.15,0:48:16.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.49,0:48:17.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.74,0:48:19.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.83,0:48:21.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.04,0:48:26.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.46,0:48:33.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.26,0:48:35.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.55,0:48:37.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.68,0:48:41.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.35,0:48:47.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.52,0:48:51.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.11,0:48:54.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.57,0:48:56.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.70,0:48:57.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.91,0:49:02.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.29,0:49:04.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.46,0:49:05.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.74,0:47:36.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.00,0:47:39.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.58,0:47:44.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不  请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.79,0:47:46.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.51,0:47:56.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失准的时钟  记录着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.52,0:48:00.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}散落满地的记忆之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.39,0:48:04.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.27,0:48:09.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看  却是那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.15,0:48:16.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.49,0:48:17.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望能与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.74,0:48:19.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.83,0:48:21.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.04,0:48:26.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不再失去曾经拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.46,0:48:33.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我忘却自己的过去  重新开始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.26,0:48:35.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不  请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.55,0:48:37.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.68,0:48:41.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿那让你苦不堪言的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.35,0:48:47.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}会迎来完结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.52,0:48:51.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我却要目送你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.11,0:48:54.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.57,0:48:56.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.70,0:48:57.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.91,0:49:02.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.29,0:49:04.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.46,0:49:05.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手迈进
